title: Need Help with Consistency?? Routine & planning / periodisation
description:
Guys I encourage planning more than anything on my podcast, but having a solid routine / planning is the key to being successful.

Better routine and better planning will lead to improved consistency in training, which inevitably will lead to improved results...
